title: Ghawre Bairey Aaj
subTitle: A contemporary retelling of the love triangle involving Nikhilesh, Sandip and Bimala.

title: Raktomukhi Neela

subTitle: Parvati feels joyful when Lord Shiva gets disguised as a woman to meet her. Mainadevi tries to convince Parvati not to marry Lord Shiva.

subTitle: Joy aspires to be a police inspector like his father, an honest police constable. As his father meets the local anti-social thug, the situation shifts and conflicts arise.

subTitle: Surya falls in love with a girl and follows her to Kolkata, where she stays with her rowdy elder brother. Later, he decides to rescue her when he discovers that a gangster wants to marry her forcibly.

subTitle: Kavita's father holds his daughter's lover's friends captive and asks them to reveal the couple's whereabouts. However, one of the boys, Abir, falls in love with his other daughter, Nandini.

subTitle: A terrible heart attack leaves Sulochana in a vulnerable position. To ease her burdens, Sulochana's daughter reaches out to her estranged husband for help.

title: Bindaas
subTitle: Abhi falls in love with Kajol and convinces her family to get them married. However, things get complicated when Kajol's uncle asks him to kill their rival's son, who is none other than Abhi himself.

subTitle: Pooja, the daughter of a ruthless businessman who cannot tolerate any male advances towards her, falls for Abir. However, when her father learns about their relationship, all hell breaks loose.

title: Badla
subTitle: Bharti Devi leads a happy life with her three sons, Jay, Sujay and Arjun. However, Sanatan decides to break their family apart in order to settle past scores with Bharti, who he believes wronged him.
